=================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                           |NAME    |
-------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR                     |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR               |:EX10002|
|2 |  └─HASH JOIN                      |        |
|3 |    ├─PART JOIN FILTER CREATE      |:RF0000 |
|4 |    │ └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|5 |    │   └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000|
|6 |    │     └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |
|7 |    │       └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1      |
|8 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR            |        |
|9 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)  |:EX10001|
|10|        └─PX BLOCK HASH JOIN-FILTER|:RF0000 |
|11|          └─TABLE RANGE SCAN       |t2(i2)  |
=================================================
