-------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                     |    |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE                  |    |
|2 |  └─SUBPLAN FILTER                     |    |
|3 |    ├─TABLE FULL SCAN                  |t3  |
|4 |    └─LIMIT                            |    |
|5 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN               |    |
|6 |        ├─DISTRIBUTED TABLE FULL SCAN  |t1  |
|7 |        └─MATERIAL                     |    |
|8 |          └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE FULL SCAN|t2  |
=================================================
